dct_description_sm: Relief shown by 20 meter contours. Drawn and photolithographed at the War Office, 1943. 10-43. 113608. Military grid (brown). Grid provisional. Includes index to railways, roads, and important buildings. North Italy Grid. Grid North is 03°39ʹW. of True North on this sheet. United States. Army Map Service In upper left margin: Italy 1:10,000. Air photographs have been used in the production of this plan." Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. no. 4380 AMS 2
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1943.
